The local convention prefers Maven-hosted `sources.jar` and `javadoc.jar` when they exist, and uses a repository tag path for tests. For Retrofit 2.5.0, Maven Central has no published test-sources/tests artifact in the directory, so I’m using the tagged GitHub test directory for `test-code-url`.
